description._content: Catalog #: 09_01966 Title: Waldeman P. Jahn Special Collection Photo Additional Information: Studio portrait of Waldeman P. Jahn in military uniform. 30 January 1945. Inscription ""hair dark, eyes hazel, Officers Forest (Wings gold)"", Waldeman P. Jahn (b. 1920) was a Naval Aviator who served during World War II and became a Commander in the United States Navy.
